She sent a coffin emoji and a bouquet emoji.
Jay snorted. You only want me dead because you know I'd leave you
Carbon when I die.
Lily must have been bored. The response was almost instantaneous.
Yes, I covet the fluffy little kitty-man. Even if his death-floof would mean the
