How's the new job?
Jay snapped a photo of her welcome bag and a Hint water she'd taken
from the fridge.
She received a champagne emoji and three confetti emojis. What about
Mr. Tall, Dark, and S.T.S.O.O.Y.?
I don't know. He's not around.
She received another text instantly but not from Lily. Looking at the
