Was she imagining the sound of his laughter? The only child to be
featured on Forbes' 30 under 30 list.
Annica was giving her an annoyed look and Jay began to feel selfconscious. She was the only one on her phone. Everyone else was hard at
work. You're going to get me in trouble. Where are you?
Look up, little bird.
