Nicholas woke up with a throbbing headache around eleven at night.
Blearily, he checked his phone, unsurprised to see that he had messages
from both his lawyers. It's over, he thought, heading down the stairs. His
eyes felt sore. Soon all of this will be over.
He made himself dinner, which he ate with a full bottle of water. He
